# Chat Mood Analyzer

## Project Overview
This project uses Natural Language Processing (NLP) techniques to analyze chat messages and predict the underlying emotion. The model classifies text into six emotion categories.

## Technologies Used
- Python
- Pandas
- Scikit-learn
- TF-IDF Vectorization
- Logistic Regression
- Matplotlib

## Features
- Text preprocessing and cleaning
- Feature extraction using TF-IDF
- Emotion classification using Logistic Regression
- Performance evaluation using accuracy scores and confusion matrix
- Visualization of model performance

